caption:
Happy New Year 2024 🎉
あけましておめでとうございます！
お風呂からご挨拶を失礼します〜 🚿🫧🧠

カメラの前で話すの、全然慣れてなくて、
これ出来上がるまで何回もトライして苦戦しててもーダメだーって思った時、
思いついたんです。

リラックスできる場所で撮影すれば普通に喋れるかもって笑
そしたらなんとか撮れました🎉
今年も皆さん、よろしくお願いします！

あと、実はこの数日間、能登半島の災害支援をお手伝いする機会があり、
そのため新年から少し遅めの投稿になりました。
とても近いお友達とご家族が被災してしまい、
私と会社マネジメントチームで現地団体と連携し、できる限りの物資提供をしていました。
伝えたい想いはたくさんありますので、後日また報告させていただにます。

しかし何よりも、皆さんの無事と一日も早く日常が戻ります様、心よりお祈り申し上げます。

2024年もみんなと一緒に過ごせることが楽しみです。☺️

Happy New Year 2024 🎉
Excuse my greeting from the bath 🚿🫧🧠

So, here's the deal: I'm not used to speaking in front of the camera. I mean, seriously, I thought this video was doomed after countless tries, but then it hit me. Maybe I can speak normally if I shoot in a place where I feel relaxed??? and voila! Managed to pull it off 🎉
Thank you all for your support this year!

Also, in the past few days, I had the opportunity to assist with earthquake disaster relief in Japan's Noto Peninsula, which is why this post is a bit delayed from the new year. Some very close friends and their families were affected, and our company's team worked with local organizations to provide as much assistance as possible. There are many thoughts and feelings I want to convey, so I will post about this on another day.

But above all, I pray from the bottom of my heart for everyone's safety and for the return of the mundane as soon as possible.

Super stoked to hang out with all of you in 2024! ☺️

#2024 #tokyo #noto #東京 #あけましておめでとう

caption:
Floral Trends 2024: A Blooming Renaissance

FLORA FORMA:
In 2024, floral prints are making their mark in the boardroom and the ballroom. Blazers and sleek suits adorned with intricate floral patterns or solids accentuated with floral patchwork or neckties are a refreshing twist to professional attire.

EMBROIDERED ELEGANCE: 
This year, embroidery takes center stage with floral designs that add texture and depth. Delicate threadwork transforms ordinary fabrics into masterpieces of floral artistry, celebrating the intricate beauty of nature with every stitch.

FUSION FLORAL: 
Ethnic wear gets a modern makeover with floral patterns in traditional Kalamkari and Ikkat textiles. This trend introduces a daring mix of sequins and embellishments, with contemporary flair for a timeless and avant-garde look.

PASTELS AND PETALS: 
Soft pastels and delicate ruffles echo the ethereal quality of flower petals. Layered, sheer fabrics in gentle hues create a romantic, dreamlike effect, perfect for those who favor a whisper of floral elegance in their attire.

CUTWORK CREATIONS: 
Cutwork styles bloom on the fashion scene, offering a beachy, crochet-inspired look. This technique uses intricate cutout designs to mimic floral patterns, creating a light and airy feel perfect for summer vibes and coastal getaways.

HUGE ABSTRACTS: 
Making a bold statement with oversized, abstract floral prints. Whether it’s a single, dramatic flower gracing an entire dress or a large-scale pattern with an artistic, painted finish, this trend is a mix of abstract minimalism with floral grandeur.

ACCESSORIES WITH A FLORAL FLARE: 
From headbands to neckties, accessories are blooming with artificial flowers this year. These playful, yet sophisticated additions add a touch of floral whimsy to any outfit, proving that sometimes, it’s the little details that make the biggest impact.
